### Create an archive

PUT http://{{host}}:{{port}}/v1/archives/{{org}}/{{proj}}/archive
Content-Type: application/ld+json

{
  "resources": [
    {
      "@type": "Resource",
      "resourceId": "http://{{host}}:{{port}}/v1/resources/{{org}}/{{proj}}/_/resource1",
      "path": "/resource1.json",
      "project": "{{org}}/{{proj}}",
      "format": "compacted"
    }
  ]
}

### Fetch an archive

GET http://{{host}}:{{port}}/v1/archives/{{org}}/{{proj}}/archive
Accept: application/ld+json

### Create an archive with originalSource

PUT http://{{host}}:{{port}}/v1/archives/{{org}}/{{proj}}/archive1
Content-Type: application/ld+json

{
  "resources": [
    {
      "@type": "Resource",
      "resourceId": "http://{{host}}:{{port}}/v1/resources/{{org}}/{{proj}}/_/resource1",
      "path": "/resource1.json",
      "project": "{{org}}/{{proj}}",
      "originalSource": true
    }
  ]
}

### Fetch an archive with original source

GET http://{{host}}:{{port}}/v1/archives/{{org}}/{{proj}}/archive1
Accept: application/ld+json

### Download an archive with Accept: application/x-tar

